 over index+relative range span lookup, with host parity tests in `tests/test_gguf_tensor_data_base.py` (WS2-04)\n--- SANHEDRIN ---\ntotal 40\ndrwxr-xr-x   7 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff   224 Apr 16 21:44 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  10 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff   320 Apr 15 16:33 ..\n-rw-r--r--   1 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff  2713 Apr 15 16:33 2026-04-12-kernel-vertical-slice-guidance.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff  1932 Apr 15 16:33 2026-04-12-llama-cpp-tokenizer-study.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff  1499 Apr 15 16:33 2026-04-12-q32-intermediate-precision.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff   881 Apr 15 18:02 2026-04-15-iq-154-wrapper-churn.md\n-rw-r--r--   1 danielmatthews-ferrero  staff  1355 Apr 16 21:44 2026-04-16-gguf-range-guard-patterns.md\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
